Ans:  17HCP + 1 for quality spade suit + 1 for adjust 3 = 19 points.

To calculate Adjust 3 on example 2: 
You have 3 Aces + 2 10's (5) and 1 Q so the total is 5 - 1 = 4 
When the total is between 3-5, add 1 point;  If the total is between 6-8, add 2. 
If it's 9 or more, you probably are opening a strong 2@C or maybe 2NT....|
