at|

Basically the responses are to 2NT are:  

Unbalanced hands:
(a) Bidding 3 of a new suit shows ^*ushortness^*N, either a singleton or void
(b) Bidding 4 of a new suit shows a ^*usecond 5 card suit^*n
(c) Bidding 4 of the agreed major shows a dead ^*uminimum^*n hand  (13-15 declarer points)

Balanced hands:
(d) Rebidding 3NT shows a balanced 5332 hand with 14-15 HCP (*)
(e) Rebidding 3 of your major shows a balanced hand with at least 16 HCP (**)|
